I do not regret shooting communist gooks. <br>
I cared about the Vietnamese people. <br>
Truth is SBARRY, you remind me of McNamara. <br>
When Robb first came to our unit, they set up a phony tent, maps and all just for a photo opportunity for him. One day all the generals, colonels, majors are out there waiting for the Secretary of Defense. The chopper with McNamara touches down. He's carrying a package. He goes by the brass reception party, doesn't bother to stop or acknowledge them, by passes them all so that he can hand deliver Lady Bird Johnson daughter's fresh baked White House wrapped cookies to Captain Charles S. Robb.   <br>
What was interesting is that they had taken some of my friends out of the jungle, wrapped them up in nice brand new lightweight jungle fatigues all for show. Soon as the party was over they were given back their old clothes and send back to the field. <br>
That's what you represent SBARRY, all phony, no substance. The damage you and individuals like Big Mc have caused to many vets is a disgrace. He now feels sorry for what he did during the war, but doesn't understand it. Feel sorry for me he writes. <br>
